      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/list/?8_1.html">潍博之讲</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?10_1.html">潍博开讲</a></div>
      <span>潍博开讲</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">“潍水讲坛·潍博开讲”第五期：孟宪钧先生金石碑帖收藏与鉴赏讲座</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px">“潍水讲坛·潍博开讲”第五期</span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">：</span></span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">孟宪钧</span></span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">先生</span></span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">金石碑帖收藏与鉴赏</span></span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">讲座</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830263784900114.jpg" title="1.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830263828796141.jpg" title="2.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px">2016年</span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px">4月16日，著名古籍善本专家孟宪钧先生为我们带来了“潍水讲坛·潍博开讲”第五期《孟宪钧：金石碑帖收藏与鉴赏》学术讲座。孟宪钧先生结合自身丰富的工作经验与专业的收藏鉴赏知识，就金石碑帖收藏历史渊源、鉴赏路径、未来前景等方面为全馆干部职工、部分志愿者、社会文物爱好者、碑帖收藏者上了一堂高质量、高水平、高层次的“金石碑帖收藏与鉴赏”的培训课。通过此次论坛开讲，既强化了广大干部职工关于金石碑帖专业知识的厚度，同时对于全馆立足于馆藏文物资源，致力于打造潍坊自身的“金石碑拓”展览品牌，也增添了信心与动力。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=191"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：<a href="/content/?190.html">“潍水讲坛·潍博开讲”第四期：邱小君先生瓷器知识</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?192.html">“潍水讲坛·潍博开讲”第六期：马杰先生古琴雅赏专题讲座</a></div>
